@section bodyheader
{
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Iotiva</h1>
            <p class="lead">A cloud scale wiring platform for the network of nouns.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
}

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
        <img class="img-circle center-block-xs " src="~/Images/Simple.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
        <h2 class="center-block-xs">Simple</h2>
        <p>Iotiva's architecture is unabashedly lean, using a few primitives as possible. We believe a Thing should define itself. We're very Zen like that.</p>
        <p><a href="#Simple" class="btn btn-default">Learn more</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
        <hr class="visible-xs">
        <img class="img-circle center-block-xs" src="~/Images/Scalable.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
        <h2 class="center-block-xs">Scalable</h2>
        <p>Iotiva is powered by Microsoft Azure providing scalability for an unfathomably large number of Things at scale. Very important if you're planning global domination.</p>
        <p><a href="#Scalable" class="btn btn-default">Learn more</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4">
        <hr class="visible-xs">
        <img class="img-circle center-block-xs" src="~/Images/Practical.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
        <h2 class="center-block-xs">Practical</h2>
        <p>Iotiva was designed with Makers and Hackers in mind, it's minimal footprint costs less than a Netflix account.</p>
        <p><a href="#Practical" class="btn btn-default">Learn more</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
<p> </p>

<div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
    Iotiva is under development so please understand that while we strive to keep things as stable and secure as possible, <strong>this cake is not baked</strong> just yet.
    I expect plenty of changes to the API as larger workloads are tested and new issues discovered.
</div>

